cu.explanation_en: Setting the AMF IP to an invalid format (octet >255) will cause IP parsing errors and connectivity failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting SSB frequency to the same as dl_absoluteFrequencyPointA causes frequency misalignment, leading to synchronization issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SSB 頻率設定為與 dl_absoluteFrequencyPointA 相同會導致頻率錯位，造成同步問題。
